trans-unit.source: Specifies the kind of application data in an email message attachment.
trans-unit.target: 指定電子郵件訊息附件中應用程式資料的類型。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application> media type designates that the attachment data should be processed by an application, such as a Postscript processor, a spreadsheet, or a word processor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application>媒體類型指定的資料應該由應用程式，例如 Postscript 處理器、 試算表或使用文書處理器來處理的附件。

trans-unit.source: The data is usually something other than simple text, such as an image, or an audio or video file.
trans-unit.target: 資料通常是簡單的文字，例如影像或音訊或視訊檔案以外的項目。

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> data is not interpreted.
The <xref:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application.Octet> member designates that the attachment contains generic binary data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application.Octet>成員指定附件包含一般的二進位資料。

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> data is in Portable Document Format (PDF).
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> 資料為 Portable Document Format (PDF) 格式。

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> data is in Rich Text Format (RTF).
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> 資料為 Rich Text Format (RTF) 格式。

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> data is a SOAP document.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> 資料為 SOAP 文件。

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the <see cref="T:System.Net.Mime.MediaTypeNames.Application" /> data is compressed.
